contenido de la variable X.

A ver si esto te sirve:

for (Y in 1:2)
{
    for (X in 3:4)
    {
        cat ("Y:", names(df)[Y], "X:", names(df)[X], "\n")
        print (summary (lm (df[,Y] ~ df[,X] + SE + ED,
                            data <- df)))
    }
}

